  "text": "CD157 regulates neutrophil and monocyte chemotaxis stimulated by fMLP and MCP-1 chemoattractant factors, respectively. Indeed, ligation of CD157 by blocking mAb resulted in impaired directional migration of both neutrophils and monocytes in conventional in vitro assays [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
